    return f"cache_{h}.jpg"
```

- `search_and_get_image()`: check cache by key first, copy downloaded image to stable key path
- `find_cached_title_image()`: use cache key lookup, return `None` (not random image) if not found
- Fall back to gradient when no cached image exists

