        "procedure": "- Jigsaw reading – 4 paragraphs. Each table is assigned 1 paragraph. Ss read write what their paragraph says in 2 sentences. 3 min. Then, rearrange the tables so that each team has 1 of the 4 paragraphs. Ss work together to get the summarized info of the other paragraphs. 8 min.\n- Reading for detail + CA – tell ss to open their books to page 111. Hand out the worksheet. Tell Ss to read the text again to decide if the sentences are true or false and to correct the false ones. Tell Ss that this will be a CA. Elicit rules. 8 min. Then, Ss swap worksheets and check each other's score. Collect scores.\n",
