  "pedagogical_justification": "Here the focus is on helping learners practice their speaking or writing skills. The overall lesson aim here will usually be something like: By the end of the lesson, learners will be better able to give their opinions on the topic of holiday destinations. By the end of the lesson, the learners will be better able to write a personal email on their everyday routines. The lesson can usually be divided into preparation for speaking/writing and speaking/writing task stages.\n",
