        "stage": "Report",
        "stage_number": 5,
        "stage_aim": "To report",
        "procedure": "- Rearrange the teams so that there is a student from each team sitting together (assign numbers).\n- In the new teams, Ss tell each other what their team decided (most common and most unusual object) 4 min.\n",
