Content and language feedback. 2 min.
```

All questions visible at once. No fragments for discussion.

### 11. Summary Slide
```markdown
## What you can do now

✓ {{ outcome_1 }}
✓ {{ outcome_2 }}
✓ {{ outcome_3 }}

Notes:
Elicit from students: What did you learn today?
Connect back to their predictions from the beginning.
```

